[3] Democratic Republic of Congo (DRC): RFI
Date: 21 Jun 2006
From: ProMED-mail <promed@promedmail.org>
Source: Polio eradication website
<http://www.polioeradication.org/content/general/casecount.pdf>

According to the polio eradication website, there have been 2 cases
of wild poliovirus polio reported in the Democratic Republic of the
Congo. Both cases are listed as importation related. The most date
of onset for the most recent case was 24 Apr 2006.
