[More information on the WPVs isolated in both the DRC and in Niger
would be greatly appreciated. Remembering that while the majority of
importation in the past 24 months have been identified as genetically
related to the WPV circulating in Nigeria, the WPV responsible for
the outbreak in Angola, and now Namibia was genetically related to
WPVs circulating in India. - Mod.MPP]
